name: Indianapolis 2020
description: The Simultaneous Interpretation team is currently looking for volunteers to serve in this essential service. Will you be at the GC Session 2020 in Indianapolis? Are you an experienced simultaneous interpreter? If you feel called to serve in this capacity, please take a few minutes and fill out our form using the link below. Please share the news of this service opportunity with other simultaneous interpreters you would recommend. We appreciate your interest and will be in touch with you soon.
